Description:
In the middle of the mangroves, you come across an old research camp. It seems to have been abandoned long ago, and the equipment is too deteriorated to be of any use. However, among the remnants of the tents, you spot a crest that looks familiar.

It resembles the crest you found in Senenthia, but it is not an exact match. Unfortunately, the symbols on the tents are too damaged to confirm any details.

It’s clear that the owners of this camp won’t be returning anytime soon, and they took anything of value with them when they left.
